        "Description" : "This is a level terrain editor for an old Macintosh RPG called \"The Odyssey\". This was my final project for my Red River College Polytechnic Java class.",
        "Instructions" : "Select the level you want to edit. On the editing screen, click the terrain you want to place, then click and drag in the editing window to place it.",
